name: Cute Kitty Stocking
description:
Very cute kitty on the ankle full length stocking! The color is gray and black. looks great with a cute dress for party!

One size: the hip area can stretch up to 40 inches.
*The measurement is taken at maximum stretch, if your own measurement is smaller, then this is the right size for you!

Hand wash in cold water. Do not put in dryer.

If you would like to buy more then one, please message me. Let me know if you have any question:)
